author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! We knew this day was coming when a massive change on Chrome browsers was arriving. Manifest V2 is finally gone and with this the best adblockers in the scene have been put to rest. You still have a choice to jump ship and keep the way you browse the Internet as safe as it's been, and here's how! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: Google Just Killed The Best Adblock...
